Phase 3: Evaluation Engine — Pillar Pipelines
Build 5 independent Python modules that consume the Interaction Trace Φ and produce normalized 0-100 pillar scores. Combined into a composite GUIDE score: Q = 0.20G + 0.25U + 0.20I + 0.15D + 0.20E.

