[NEW] 
pillar_u.py
Metric	How	Source
PSS (Prompt Specificity)	LLM-as-Judge: rate each prompt 1-10 on clarity, context, actionability	PROMPT events + LLM call
PPF (Prompts-per-Feature)	total_prompts / features_implemented, scored against 1.5-2.5 range	PROMPT + TEST_RUN events
CIR (Context Injection Rate)	prompts_referencing_code / total_prompts, target >70%	PROMPT + CODE_SAVE events
