Step 3.3 — Pillar I: Iteration & Refinement
[NEW] 
pillar_i.py
Metric	How	Source
ERS (Error Recovery Speed)	Avg prompts between failed and next passing TEST_RUN, 1/avg_turns, normalize vs 3-turn benchmark	TEST_RUN + PROMPT events
